data.description: Welcome to Stream Valley Court located in THE PRESERVE AT AYDELOTTE FARM. Upon entry you are greeted by a wide open floor plan accented with LVP flooring, stainless appliances and plenty of natural light. Owners suite, two additional bedrooms and laundry are on the second floor of the home with a full bathroom. Plenty of storage throughout the home. Just off the dining area is a sizable outdoor patio overlooking the rear fenced back yard. This Home is equipped with a complete smart Home package. Plenty of room to entertain family and friends or sip your favorite beverage while relaxing in your private hot tub. Call today to make this house your Home!
